== How to use FixtureReplacement

Coming soon, when time permits.  For now, watch this screencast (and forward
through my stupidity):

http://railsnewbie.com/files/fixture_replacement_demo.mov


== Running the Specs/Tests

You will need rspec (version 1.0.8 or later) to run the specs:

  sudo gem install rspec


